SUMMARY:Glorious Civilizations: An Exploration of Southeast Asia
DESCRIPTION:Registration is required. Sign up below to receive the Zoom 
 information on the morning of the event. \n\nEleven countries\, thousands 
 of years\, millions of people: explore the cultures of Southeast Asia as 
 reflected in secular and religious artworks from this fascinating region. 
 This program features objects from the collection of the Asian Art Museum\, 
 including sculptures from Angkor Wat in Cambodia\; Buddhas from Myanmar and 
 Thailand\; ceramics from Vietnam\; and textiles from the 
 Philippines.\n\nPresented by the Asian Art Museum.\n\n\n\nThis event is 
 generously sponsored by the Friends of the Mountain View Library.
LOCATION:Online
ORGANIZER;CN="Kyle Hval":MAILTO:kyle.hval@mountainview.gov
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts (Adult), Science & History
UID:LibCal-8800-15891656
URL:https://mountainview.libcal.com/event/15891656
END:VEVENT
