SUMMARY:Zentangle Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Registration is required. Seats and materials are limited. 
 Please only register if you plan on attending.\n\nDiscover the Zentangle 
 Method\, an easy-to-learn\, relaxing\, and fun way to create beautiful 
 images by drawing structured patterns. This beginner-friendly workshop 
 introduces participants to a creative practice that encourages focus\, 
 mindfulness\, and a calm approach to drawing.\n\nNo artistic experience is 
 needed\, and all materials will be provided.\n\nThis class is intended for 
 adults\, ages 18 and up only.\n\n\n\nThis event is generously sponsored by 
 the Friends of the Mountain View Library.
LOCATION:1st Floor Program Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Kyle Hval":MAILTO:kyle.hval@mountainview.gov
