SUMMARY:STEAM Fridays
DESCRIPTION:\n\nGet ready to tinker\, build\, explore\, and create!\n\nJoin 
 us for STEAM Fridays\, a drop-in program full of hands-on activities that 
 spark curiosity and creativity. Whether you're a budding scientist\, an 
 imaginative engineer\, or an artistic innovator\, there’s something for 
 everyone to discover.\n\nEach week features a variety of self-directed 
 projects in Science\, Technology\, Engineering\, Art\, and Math\, perfect 
 for curious minds who love to experiment and play.\n\n\n\nSome projects 
 might get a little messy. Please dress appropriately.\n\n \n\n\n\nThis 
 event is generously sponsored by the Friends of the Mountain View Library.
LOCATION:1st Floor Program Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Renee Kitson":MAILTO:renee.kitson@mountainview.gov
