SUMMARY:Needle Crafts Circle
DESCRIPTION:Join our needle crafts circle and enjoy a relaxed\, friendly 
 space for all fabric arts—hand sewing\, knitting\, crocheting\, and more. 
 Bring your project and unwind with a welcoming community of fellow 
 crafters.\n\nNo registration required. Seating is limited and available on 
 a first come\, first served basis. The needle crafts circle is intended for 
 adults\, ages 18 and up.\n\nThe needle crafts circle meets on the 4th 
 Saturday of every month. \n
LOCATION:2nd Floor Program Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Charles Mosner":MAILTO:charles.mosner@mountainview.gov
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts (Adult)
