SUMMARY:Bad Art Night: Disaster-piece Theater
DESCRIPTION:Get creative — and gloriously messy! Join us for Bad Art\, 
 where teens and tweens can paint\, glue\, doodle\, and design the 
 silliest\, weirdest masterpieces imaginable. No art skills required — the 
 worse it looks\, the better! Snacks will be provided for participants\, and 
 the worst creation wins a trophy.\n\nFor teens grades 6-12.
LOCATION:1st Floor Program Room
