SUMMARY:Positive Mindset Sound Bath
DESCRIPTION:Seating is limited. Registration is recommended. Walk-ins are 
 also welcome.\n\nPositive Mindset Sound Bath is an immersive experience 
 designed to help quiet emotional noise\, regulate the nervous system\, and 
 reconnect you with a calmer\, clearer state of being.\n\nThrough guided 
 meditation and immersive sound\, we create intentional space to reflect on 
 the patterns\, mindset\, and energy shaping our daily lives while 
 reconnecting with the habits\, clarity\, and inner direction we want to 
 cultivate more consciously. When the mind becomes quieter\, we often gain a 
 deeper awareness of ourselves: how we think\, how we move through life\, 
 and who we want to become.\n\nLed by Charlotte Zhang\, founder of Inner 
 Tone Sound Healing Center in Los Altos\, this experience is inspired by her 
 work supporting many Bay Area professionals navigating stress\, burnout\, 
 emotional overwhelm\, and disconnection from themselves in the midst of 
 demanding modern lifestyles.\n \n\n\n\nThis event is generously sponsored 
 by the Friends of the Mountain View Library.
LOCATION:1st Floor Program Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Kyle Hval":MAILTO:kyle.hval@mountainview.gov
CATEGORIES:Health & Wellness
UID:LibCal-8800-16571149
URL:https://mountainview.libcal.com/event/16571149
