 program is for all. Feel free to bring a fold out chair\, towel\, or 
 blanket for your comfort out in the park. Light refreshments will be 
 provided.\n\nThis class is intended for adults\, ages 18 and up 
 only.\n\n\n\nThis event is generously sponsored by the Friends of the 
 Mountain View Library.
