SUMMARY:Tech Take Apart
DESCRIPTION:\n\nCurious about what’s inside a computer? Join us for this 
 hands-on program where kids can take apart e-waste like CPUs\, monitors\, 
 and mice to discover how computers work. Learn about the different parts 
 and how they come together before recycling them responsibly. Perfect for 
 young tech explorers.\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n\n \n\nThis event is 
 generously sponsored by the Friends of the Mountain View Library.
