 Public Library on Mercy St.\n\nSaturday\n9:30 am - 10:30am Members-only 
 Sale\n\n10:30 am - 4:00 pm General Public Sale\n\nSunday\n\n11:00 am – 
 2:00 pm Fill-a-Bag Sale\n\n2:00 pm - 4:00 pm Bulk Sale $1 per foot 
 length\n\n\n\nFor more information about the book sale and how to support 
 the Friends of the Mountain View Library\, \n\nclick here to visit their 
 website!\n\n\n\n
